{"type": "article", "id": 12930, "title": "盐水供电的灯具", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-03T07:39:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061405208TCkIzJUFuAdV9BW.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t菲律宾经常遭遇台风，地震等灾害，由此引起的停电给当地人带来了很大的麻烦。于是，工程师  Aisa Mijena 最近设计了一款用盐水供电的灯具，没错，不需要任何电池，电线，插座等等，只需要一杯盐水，甚至是菲律宾最常见的海水都可以，就可以让灯持续点亮八小时，此外，灯具还配备了一个 USB 接口，可以用来给手机充电。根据设计，这款灯有很强的耐用度，如果持续浸泡在盐水里面，几乎能不更换零件地用上一年左右。目前这个款灯正在推广阶段，<a href=\"http://www.salt.ph/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以前往他们的官网查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140614UXjE20JIdzthHkRg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140614zfpFMXqSRHQK0agd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140615uwnWvAF3NzgPheXD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614061540gfhyP182eRY9n5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56122449\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140616rSo6cLExKwbuvPd2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140616J0KNcMkDnEZIh2X7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}